  Name: Third Person View
  Version: 1.0
  MinMFPSVersion: 1.8
  Instructions: "This addon allows the use of the <b>Third Person View</b> in MFPS.\r\n\r\nYou
    can enable the option so players can switch between <b>first-person</b> and <b>third-person</b>
    view in-game with a button or set the third-person view as the unique game view
    in case you want to use MFPS for a Third Person Shooter.\r\n\r\nThe integration
    is <b>2-clicks</b> only:\r\n\n\u2589 <b>Enable the addon:</b> Go to MFPS -> Addons
    -> Third Person -> Enable.\n\u2589 <b>Setup the players:</b> Go to MFPS -> Addons
    -> Third Person -> Integrate.\n\n\u257E You can change the default player view
    <i>(third person or first person)</i> in <i>Assets->Addons->ThirdPersonView->Resources-><b>CameraViewSettings</b>->Game
    Player View</i>.\n\n<b>The default key to switch views is <b><size=18>P</size></b></b>"
  TutorialScript: MFPSTPViewDocumentation
